{"image_id": "SBAC_2011_page_16", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 90.6, 206.4, 119.3]}, {"text": "The following is a list of significant customers (representing at least 10% of revenue in any of the last three years) and the percentage of", "bbox": [85.5, 143.2, 1225.7, 170.8]}, {"text": "our total revenues for the specified time periods derived from these customers:", "bbox": [37.5, 166.4, 703.4, 194.1]}, {"text": "We also have client concentrations with respect to revenues in each of our financial reporting segments:", "bbox": [85.5, 389.9, 961.9, 417.6]}, {"text": "Revenue from these clients is derived from numerous different site leasing contracts and site development contracts. Each site leasing", "bbox": [85.5, 1006.2, 1205.4, 1033.8]}, {"text": "contract relates to the lease of space at an individual tower site and is generally for an initial term of five years renewable for five 5-year", "bbox": [37.5, 1029.2, 1178.2, 1056.8]}, {"text": "periods at the option of the tenant. However, if any of our significant site leasing clients were to experience financial difficulty, substantially", "bbox": [37.5, 1052.2, 1213.7, 1079.8]}, {"text": "reduce their capital expenditures or reduce their dependence on leased tower space and fail to renew their leases with us, our revenues, future", "bbox": [37.5, 1075.2, 1219.2, 1102.8]}, {"text": "revenue growth and results of operations would be adversely affected.", "bbox": [37.5, 1098.4, 632.2, 1126.1]}, {"text": "Our site development customers engage us on a project-by-project basis, and a customer can generally terminate an assignment at any", "bbox": [85.5, 1140.2, 1207.2, 1167.8]}, {"text": "time without penalty. In addition, a customer’s need for site development services can decrease, and we may not be successful in establishing", "bbox": [37.5, 1163.2, 1221.9, 1190.8]}, {"text": "relationships with new customers. Furthermore, our existing customers may not continue to e